• <WEBSITENAME>According to the affiliate agreement, the commission will be paid monthly in proportion to the dividend. On the first Monday of each month, the agent’s commission feedback for the previous calendar month will be settled. And within five working days after settlement, they will be uniformly distributed to the bank account. After monthly settlement, if the agent’s total commission is lower than the threshold, the current commission will remain in the account and will accumulate to the next month’s settlement, and the commission rebate will accumulate to It can be withdrawn above the threshold. If the agent’s total commission has a "negative value", it will be accumulated to the next month and combined.
  • The promotion of the rebate ratio must meet the two conditions of "Current Month Payout" and "Valid Membership" at the same time.
    For example, if the agent pays 400,000 lottery in the current month, but the effective number of people is less than 20, the commission rate will be calculated based on the 30% level.
  • The name of the cooperative agent must be consistent with the payee’s bank account and name, otherwise has the right to request the cooperative agent to provide a valid certification file for identity verification.
  • <WEBSITENAME> will review the effectiveness of the monthly agent promotion. If there are less than 5 active members for more than 3 months, it will be deemed to have suspended the agent qualification; if you want to re-agent, please contact the agent specialist to discuss .
  • <WEBSITENAME>In the monthly settlement, the agent will be asked to verify the information, and the agent must provide the real contact information. If there is no agent that provides the verification in the current month, the commission will only be retained until the next month's settlement! Those who have not received it overdue shall be deemed to have waived the commission qualification!
